title: Angry Birds Seasons 4.0.1 for PC [Latest] + Patch
description:
Description:
Angry Birds Seasons takes the captivating gameplay of the original to a whole new level! From Halloween to Chinese New Year, the birds are celebrating different festive seasons around the world! With more than 300 levels these special episodes offer more challenging levels of pig-popping action and golden eggs to discover.


What's New in Version 4.0.1 (09 Dec, 2013) :
Pack your bags for an Arctic Eggspedition with 25 festive, frosty, and fun-filled levels! Plus 4 bonus levels!
NEW FROSTY LEVELS! Get in the festive spirit with 25 advent calendar levels Ã¢â‚¬â€œ one for each day before Christmas! Plus get 4 bonus levels!
NEW ARCTIC THEME! Take an Arctic Eggspedition and face sub-zero temperatures, large blocks of ice and some rather cold piggies!


Minimum System Requirements:
OS Windows XP SP3
RAM 512MB
CPU 1GHz
Graphic OpenGL 1.3 compatible


Install Notes:
1) Install the game.
2) Run "angry.birds.all-patch.offline.v1.4.exe" from Patch folder.
3) Click Patch button and browse to main game folder & select main game executable. 
[For ex. , if you want to crack 'Angry Birds Seasons', select "Angry Birds Seasons.EXE"]
4) Register the game with: ABCD-EFGH-IJKL-MNOP
5) Enjoy! :)
